formattedAddress: 1949 The Hidden City, Courtyard 4, Gongti Bei Lu, Chaoyang district (at 1949 The Hidden City)

tip.text: Cakes are good, but on the busy days/time, service is slow (junior staff) and the place quite noisy...
Not sure it's yet the largest selection on tap, but bottled included, definitely the largest selection of craftbeer in Singapore.
Burgers have a good but fair size, so that not only you don't feel guilty after finishing one of these succulent things, but you can also safely upgrade to a double or even have a second one  :)
Bit busy during the weekend, but definitely worth the wait !
Good comfort food, and nice selection of beers including Punk IPA :p
Italian gourmet, good selection of wine, fine pastries, what else to add ? Oh yes, they also have cronut !
